          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1642065415856-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausages have browned, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span><strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and add your <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> – this is your <strong>Henderson's stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1642065428062-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1642065428062-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1642065428062-x700.jpg",
